Commentary: OUT! RUN OUT! After a long struggle, Bangladesh finally breaks the partnership! On the pads, fuller and Kavem Hodge flicks the ball straight to Taijul Islam at deep square leg and looks for a single but is denied by his partner. Taijul Islam throws the ball straight to Litton Das and he takes the bails off in time. The Third Umpire is convinced as Kavem Hodge is well short of the ground. Kavem Hodge walks back after scoring 25 (63) and the West Indies are 84/3.
Default_Commentary: 37.3: Mehidy Hasan to Kavem Hodge, OUT! run out (Taijul Islam / Litton Das).
Howout: run out (Taijul Islam / Litton Das)

A bye taken and more importantly it will be Taskin Ahmed on strike for the next over!
Default_Commentary: 37.6: Jayden Seales to Taskin Ahmed, Bye.
